trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<wsFederation>" name="<wsFederation>" href=""></xref> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerer den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<wsFederation>" name="<wsFederation>" href=""> </xref> element i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The `<wsFederation>` element provides configuration for the WS-Federation Authentication Module (WSFAM), which is represented by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule> class.
trans-unit.target: Den `<wsFederation>` -elementet har konfigurasjonen for WS Federation godkjenning modulen (WSFAM), som er representert av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>klasse.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Services.WSFederationAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: The properties of the WSFederationElement class represent the attributes of the `<wsFederation>` element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskaper for klassen WSFederationElement representerer attributtene for den `<wsFederation>` elementet.
